{"tid":1258329,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［純討論］講開眾籌，點解唔眾籌買地建港","createTime":"2019-06-26T05:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T03:35:17.000Z","uid":217184,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12573ad7f9f8d06a46d4915d859730db33343f3a","tid":1258329,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"琴日眾籌登報<br />\n3個鐘入內，有1萬捐300萬。<br />\n如果我地眾籌買地建港又有冇可能？<br />\n<br />\n倪匡係89年已經提出想關concept<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KingOfCaptureHK/videos/460789084695694/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKingOfCaptureHK%2Fvideos%2F460789084695694%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmTbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=f312b317\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KingOfCaptureHK/videos/460789084695694/</a><br />\n<br />\n依家呢幾年又有人放地<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/9889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F9889&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmTbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=fac7664f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/9889</a><br />\n<br />\n100百萬人捐1000千蚊已經10億<br />\n又或者拎明日大愚嘅錢嚟買都可以<br />\n<br />\n利申唔係分化L<br />\n雖然我哋喺經濟上面都有好多考慮（一搬無曬依家優勢～）<br />\n但大家都知呢一仗係最終一役<br />\n一輸就收得皮 咁我地都應該plan好一切<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecefc8655926ce2b6517382fb5c464b7bc1d404","tid":1258329,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"因為唔想送幾萬億俾維尼駛,要死一齊死,焦Q維尼土."},{"pid":"ec375bfe2f95569cb891b74784cadb3fd30704bc","tid":1258329,"uid":40623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"重要預埋d 錢for基建<br />\n又要預時間發展當地經濟<br />\n冇返30~40年都搞唔掂"},{"pid":"1d2e123702fdbd9dc0053318e1faeec1b89c2fdd","tid":1258329,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"巴打講得啱<br />\n要搬地就要預左時間同資金發展經濟<br />\n但其實個情況咪同自己個人搬出嚟住類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係要預留資金<br />\n<br />\n雖然一開始要比按金同租金<br />\n但搬出嚟住有更大嘅自由度<br />\n家俬果啲咪逐件買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ade188d0a2c3055801d7e6050974be47e4d8dd6","tid":1258329,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"屌你買地建國講傢俬<br />\n你估sim咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基建已經用好撚多錢<br />\n除非你想做返原始人<br />\n地點分又係個問題 錢有人出多有人出少<br />\n<br />\n建國就唔會work架啦<br />\n最有錢個啲人自組村落都有得諗下既"}]}